# THIS IS A SAMPLE HOSTS FILE
#
# THIS FILE CONTAINS THE MAPPINGS OF IP ADDRESSES THAT ARE LINKED TO HOSTNAMES
#
# ANY WEBSITE THAT IS INCLUDED IN THIS FILE WILL
# PREVENT THE USER FROM VISITING IT BY
# LINKING THAT WEBSITE HOSTNAME TO OUR LOCALHOST IP ADRESS OF 127.0.0.1 
# SINCE THERE IS NOTHING RUNNING IN THE LOCALHOST, IT WILL RETURN AN ERROR AND WILL NOT LOAD THE PAGE
#
# Host Database
#
# localhost is used to configure the loopback interface
# when the system is booting.
##
127.0.0.1	localhost
255.255.255.255	broadcasthost
::1             localhost

127.0.0.1 www.facebook.com
127.0.0.1 facebook.com
